extends userBase.pug

block title
    h1(style='font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; margin: 16px 0;') Hello #{name}

block content
    p(style='font-size: 18px; margin: 8px 0;') You might've forgotten to verify your email address! Best to do it as soon as possible so you don't miss out on free comics
    p(style='font-size: 18px; margin: 8px 0;') If you've created your account by a mistake and wish to delete it, respond to this email with "DELETE" 
